             were indicted for that <rs id="t17840526-118-off524" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840526-118-off524" type="offenceCategory" value="breakingPeace"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840526-118-off524" type="offenceSubcategory" value="assault"></interp>
               they, with one 
                     <persName id="t17840526-118-person1038">
                        James
                         Barron
                     <interp inst="t17840526-118-person1038" type="surname" value="Barron"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17840526-118-person1038" type="given" value="James"></interp>
