                  , and divers other persons, to the number of three hundred, and more on the <rs id="t17840526-118-cd525" type="crimeDate">30th day of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840526-118-off524 t17840526-118-cd525"></join> last with force and arms, unlawfully, riotously, and tumultuously, did assemble together, to the disturbance of the public peace, and with force and arms feloniously, unlawfully, and with force, did begin to demolish and pull down a certain dwelling house of one 
                     <persName id="t17840526-118-victim1039" type="victimName">
                        Dominick 
                        Adlum
                     <interp inst="t17840526-118-victim1039" type="surname" value="Adlum"></interp>
